1494/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ad8102379cb463bd861b7d623f813a4044563a67","tid":1411471,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"大家喺附近如果見到愉景新城有咩奇怪嘢，唔使屌啲職員，瘋狂咁去通知田北辰，佢成日話自己只做實事唔玩政治，我哋就不停用街坊嘅名義叫佢處理跟進。"},{"pid":"bda742bf71b62f76833429d46e50d6ed61159799","tid":1411471,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"入愉景好撚大鑊，細路多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑狗想死就爆入去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f2a96f4ba0f266a2012166dadada959e2928f1","tid":1411471,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76610aaccbc2f0aa6cf7e98a861508754500960d","tid":1411471,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34f2a96f4ba0f266a2012166dadada959e2928f1","tid":1411471,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44a0a3a24522d400d8083a6cc571315dfdb5a03","tid":1411471,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"大家唔好攪巴士站隔離既露天停車場，警察叔叔要對付暴徒己經好累，返工攪到要比埋錢整車嫁就好慘嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"ae19ecf24dfbd0a26c5f1df278b4c3d3cc86ab2f","tid":1411471,"uid":48624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"愉景新城商場近警署各層的出入口嘅玻璃門全部鎖淨一道門，並貼上&quot;工程進行中&quot;"}]}